Felt like some electrical wave went through me.

139
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:27,570
我想这就是那个武器了
I think that was the thing.

140
00:11:34,160 --> 00:11:36,000
干得漂亮 凯文 大家干得都漂亮
Well done, Kevin. Well done, crew.

141
