Yes. Out of respect.

161
00:13:19,520 --> 00:13:21,980
他就像我的家人一样 我的意思是…
He's the closest thing I have to family. I mean…

162
00:13:23,190 --> 00:13:24,480
除了你以外
After you now.

163
00:13:25,150 --> 00:13:26,150
好吧
Okay.

164
00:13:28,860 --> 00:13:32,490
小莱拉和奥斯威勒先生来了 他们想见你
Lilah Junior and Mr. Osweiller are here to see you.

165
00:13:32,570 --> 00:13:33,660
